Warhead raises his optics. He looked staight up... and saw the floor. 
Other transformers who have wondered how they had gotten in such a 
position or would have panicked. They were cowards.

Warhead: WHAT THE SLAG IS THIS JOKE???? I SWEAR BY WHATEVER REMAINS OF 
UNICRON THAT I WILL SLAY THE ONE RESPONSIBLE FOR THIS!!!!

He then heard Megatron's call and realized they had crashed. He 
twisted around and banged on the ceiling several times, thus freeing 
himself and crashing hard on the floor. He checked around and 
remembered he was in the engine room.

Warhead: If anyone's here, I'm going to the bridge.

He walked out and went for the bridge. He barely found his way, so 
being unused the the maximal design of the freighter. He arrived after 
a few moments and walked near the command chair.

Warhead: I have arrived, Megatron. What orders do you have?
